---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="会社概要 | 株式会社SBT">
  <div class="bg-slate-50 py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-10 border-l-8 border-yellow-500 pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Company</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-300 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-12">
        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
          <tbody>
            {[
              { label: "社名", value: "株式会社ＳＢＴ" },
              { label: "設立", value: "2015年6月3日" },
              { label: "代表取締役", value: "柴田 雄介" },
              { label: "所在地", value: "〒170-0011 東京都豊島区池袋本町4-11-1" },
              { label: "連絡先", value: "TEL：03-6912-8306 / FAX：03-6912-8307" },
              { label: "事業内容", value: "コンピュータシステム開発 / ITコンサルティング / ネットワーク構築・運用保守" }
            ].map((row, index) => (
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 last:border-b-0">
                <th class="w-1/3 md:w-1/4 bg-slate-50 p-4 md:p-6 text-[12px] md:text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                  {row.label}
                </th>
                <td class="p-4 md:p-6 text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium whitespace-pre-wrap">
                  {row.value}
                </td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-10 border-l-8 border-yellow-500 pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Access</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-300 rounded-lg shadow-md p-2">
        <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-slate-100 rounded md:h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3238.932311440051!2d139.70773667635687!3d35.73907402672323!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x60188d5598688755%3A0x6b82531065f97984!2z44CSMTcwLTAwMTEg5p2x5Lqs6YO96LGK5bO25Yy65rGg6KKL5pys55S677yU5LiB55uu77yR77yR4oiS77yR!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1710000000000!5m2!1sja!2sjp" 
            class="w-full h-full border-0" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 md:p-6 text-sm text-slate-500 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
          最寄り駅：東武東上線「北池袋駅」徒歩2分 / JR線「池袋駅」徒歩15分
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>